text: Kinney National Service Inc. was a media company formed in 1961 formed from a joint venture between Riverside Memorial Home and Kinney Parking System. It went through another merger with National Cleaning Company in 1966. Produced movie studios including Warner Bros. Pictures, television companies including Warner Bros. Television. In 1972, Kinney National Company spun off its non- media assets and reorganized itself into Warner Communications.
